# PyDisk
PyDisk is a python module to get all physical drives connected to a host machine.

## Installation

```shell
pip install PyDisk
```

## Usage

```python
import pydisk

if __name__ == '__main__':
    all_disks = pydisk.get_all_disks()
    print(all_disks)
```
